snippet.title: Hazard Pay - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now: https://smitner.studio/hp?utm_source=youtube

In this dark and mysterious block-pushing puzzler, you'll navigate through a secret, hazardous laboratory complex. Discover creative methods to destroy evidence and cover up the crimes of your employer. 

------
Attribution:
Music,  "Murder on the Metrorail" by joeBaxterWebb
